TITLE: Creating Documents with Circular References in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Example of creating documents with circular references using the defined schema in Convex.
SOURCE: https://github.com/get-convex/convex-backend/blob/main/npm-packages/docs/docs/database/schemas.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_12

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
