TITLE: Defining DataModelFromSchemaDefinition Type in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: A TypeScript type that creates a data model from a schema definition. It transforms table definitions into a structured data model with documents, field paths, and index information.
SOURCE: https://github.com/get-convex/convex-backend/blob/main/npm-packages/convex/api-extractor-configs/reports/server.api.md#2025-04-21_snippet_16

