TITLE: Context Interface Definitions
DESCRIPTION: Interface definitions for action, mutation and query contexts
SOURCE: https://github.com/get-convex/convex-backend/blob/main/npm-packages/convex/api-extractor-configs/reports/server.api.md#2025-04-21_snippet_31

